metadata.name: Aren't Completely Gentrified
metadata.description: West Dallas aka Oakcliff is home to some of Dallas' most beloved graffiti artists. The area known as the Fabrication Yard is currently being bought up and turned into artists' lofts in an attempt to slowly "develop" the neighborhood into a high-value area. The main character of this particular piece features an anti-gentrification poster that was wheat-pasted onto a building in protest of these recent developments. The poster said, "Make sure West Dallas and her art aren't completely gentrified."
